{"an5.42:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.42 ","an5.42:0.2":"5. Mundarajavagga ","an5.42:0.3":"Sappurisasutta ","an5.42:1.1":"“Sappuriso, bhikkhave, kule jayamano bahuno janassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:1.2":"matapitunam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:1.3":"puttadarassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:1.4":"dasakammakaraporisassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:1.5":"mittamaccanam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:1.6":"samanabrahmananam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti. ","an5.42:2.1":"Seyyathapi, bhikkhave, mahamegho sabbasassani sampadento bahuno janassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.2":"evamevam kho, bhikkhave, sappuriso kule jayamano bahuno janassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.3":"matapitunam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.4":"puttadarassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.5":"dasakammakaraporisassa atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.6":"mittamaccanam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hoti; ","an5.42:2.7":"samanabrahmananam atthaya hitaya sukhaya hotiti. ","an5.42:3.1":"Hito bahunnam patipajja bhoge, ","an5.42:3.2":"Tam devata rakkhati dhammaguttam; ","an5.42:3.3":"Bahussutam silavatupapannam, ","an5.42:3.4":"Dhamme thitam na vijahati kitti. ","an5.42:4.1":"Dhammattham silasampannam, ","an5.42:4.2":"saccavadim hirimanam; ","an5.42:4.3":"Nekkham jambonadasseva, ","an5.42:4.4":"ko tam ninditumarahati; ","an5.42:4.5":"Devapi nam pasamsanti, ","an5.42:4.6":"brahmunapi pasamsito”ti. ","an5.42:4.7":"Dutiyam. "}